<sect2>
<title>Installation de <application><acronym>GNOME</acronym> Session</application></title>

<para>Installez <application><acronym>GNOME</acronym> Session</application> en lançant les
commandes suivantes:</para>

<screen><userinput><command>export PATH=$PATH:$GNOME_PREFIX/sbin:/sbin &amp;&amp;
./configure --prefix=$GNOME_PREFIX --localstatedir=/var/lib \
--sysconfdir=/etc/gnome  &amp;&amp;
make &amp;&amp;
make install</command></userinput></screen>

</sect2>

